name: Toast of Tinseltown
overview: Tortured thespian Steven Toast relocates to the ultimate actor's playground - Hollywood. Surely this time he will get the adulation he so richly deserves.

episodes.name: Anger Man
episodes.overview: After a successful visit to an anger management centre, Toast is a new man and sets about apologising to all the people he's been rude to. However, when he reveals the extent of his wrongdoing to Purchase, the pair come face to face at the Colonial Club.

episodes.name: LA Story
episodes.overview: Toast gets offered his first part in a major Hollywood film, but will he get through the increasingly bizarre auditions?

episodes.name: The Scorecard
episodes.overview: Russ is far from pleased that Toast is going on a date with glamorous sexologist, Shepherd Gerbil, but Toast is smitten despite her rather clinical lovemaking.

episodes.name: Doctor Grainger
episodes.overview: After attending a 'doctor acting' masterclass by Richard Chickentoss, Toast lands the role of a doctor in a successful hospital soap alongside Latina singing sensation, Carmen.

episodes.name: Death Valley
episodes.overview: Toast has been signed up to star in a Western. However, after a very bumpy trailer ride Toast finds himself marooned in the desert and no sign of anybody else from the crew.
